# Auto Push

After any schedule or site change in this project, automatically commit and push to `main` without waiting for the user to ask.

- Commit with a concise message describing what changed
- Push to `origin/main` (deploys GitHub Pages)
- Briefly confirm the commit hash and site URL in the reply

Do not push secrets or credential files.
